Context:
The George Brown College Foundation welcomes third-party events to support their fundraising efforts. Interested parties should fill out the Third Party Event Procedures form and contact Samantha Walker at samantha.walker@georgebrown.ca or 416-415-5000 x3005 for assistance. The key to a successful event includes planning, budgeting, promoting the event, and ensuring everyone involved knows their responsibilities. For more information about application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, and tours, sign up on their website. Contact numbers are 416-415-2000 and TTY: 1-877-515-5559. Their email is ask.george@georgebrown.ca and social media hub can be found on their website. The information contained in the website is subject to change without notice.
